<!-- A shout out to LifeChurch.tv for designing a great giving area that we are imitating. --><h2>Giving at Portland Christian Center</h2><p>You&rsquo;ve got options when you&rsquo;re deciding how to give to Portland Christian Center. Choose the method that best supports your giving goals and lifestyle.</p><hr><div class="giving-top-left"><a class="button" target="_blank" href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/nonmemberlogin.aspx?sn=1233&amp;sc=give">Login to Give</a><h5>Why create an account?</h5><p>Set up scheduled giving <br>Designate gifts to specific causes<br>Easily track &amp; adjust your giving 24/7</p></div><div class="giving-top-right"><a href="https://pcctalks.wufoo.com/forms/online-giving-onetime/" class="button" target="_blank">Give via Paypal</a><h5>No account? No problem.</h5><p>Make a quick one-time donation<br>You'll still receive a statement</p></div><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><div class="giving-tri"><a href="#on-site"><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2251701&amp;fileName=graphic--giving--on-site-giving-circle-0-0-200-200.png" width="200" height="200" alt="GRAPHIC : GIVING : On-site Giving Circle" title="GRAPHIC : GIVING : On-site Giving Circle"></a> <a href="#online"><img src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/g/0e2230367_1371677542_graphic--giving--online-giving-circle.png"></a> <a href="#non-cash"><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2251737&amp;fileName=graphic--giving--non-cash-giving-circle-0-0-200-200.png" width="200" height="200" alt="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Non-Cash Giving Circle" title="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Non-Cash Giving Circle"></a></div><p><img src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/g/0e2232247_1371684825_graphic--giving--on-site-giving-large-rectangle.jpg" alt="GRAPHIC : GIVING : On-site Giving - Large Rectangle" title="GRAPHIC : GIVING : On-site Giving - Large Rectangle" class="giving-img-left"></p><div class="giving-right-col"><h3 id="on-site">On-Site Giving</h3><p class="highlight">You can make your gifts in person using cash, checks, or debit/credit cards.</p><p>While you&rsquo;re attending service at Portland Christian Center, you can use giving envelopes found in the back of your seats. Our giving envelopes are an easy and safe way to give by cash, check, or even a credit card/debit card.</p><p>You can always drop off or mail a check to the church office at:</p><p>Portland Christian Center<br> 5700 SW Dosch Rd<br> Portland, Oregon 97239<br> 503-245-7735</p></div><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><div class="giving-left-col"><h3 id="online">Online Giving</h3><p class="highlight">By setting up an online account you can give tithes and offerings in several ways:</p><ul><li>Use a credit or debit card</li><li>Link directly to a bank account</li><li>Setup &amp; manage recurring gifts</li><li>And even track your giving history</li></ul><p>If you don't have an account, you can also quickly give a one-time donation.</p><p><a href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/nonmemberlogin.aspx?sn=1233&amp;sc=give" class="button">Set up an account</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://pcctalks.wufoo.com/forms/online-giving-onetime/" class="button">One-time donation</a></p></div><p><img src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/g/0e2232553_1371672646_graphic--giving--online-giving-large-rectangle.jpg" alt="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Online Giving - Large Rectangle" title="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Online Giving - Large Rectangle" class="giving-img-right"></p><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><p><img src="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/g/0e2232813_1371677922_graphic--giving--non-cash-giving-large-rectangle.jpg" alt="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Non-Cash Giving - Large Rectangle" title="GRAPHIC : GIVING : Non-Cash Giving - Large Rectangle" class="giving-img-left"></p><div class="giving-right-col"><h3 id="non-cash">Non-Cash Giving</h3><p class="highlight">Did you know you can donate non-cash gifts like stocks, bonds, mutual funds, or cars? There are many other ways to give:</p><ul><li><strong>Marketable Securities</strong>: transfer ownership of your stocks, bonds, or mutual fund shares</li><li><strong>Non-Cash Items</strong>: donate items like cars, boats, and jewelry</li><li>Life Insurance: name the church as a beneficiary</li><li><strong>Planned Gifts</strong>: give via retirement assets, trusts, etc. as part of your overall personal financial strategy (including an IRA Charitable Rollover, which allows IRA owners over 70.5 years to transfer up to $100,000 per year to charities).</li><li><strong>Online Shopping</strong>: purchase through our links online and the church receive a percentage of your purchase - <a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/extras/amazoncom-gives-back-to-pcc/">Amazon.com</a> &amp; <a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/christianbookcom-gives-back/">ChristianBooks.com</a></li></ul></div><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><hr><p>If you are interested in any of these types of giving or have any questions, please contact the Chief Stewardship Officer, Ron Stokes, at <script type='text/javascript'>var u1756527447='rstokes'; var h1579790968='pcctoday.com';var linktext=u1756527447+'@'+h1579790968;h1579790968='pcctoday.com';document.write('<a href=' + 'mail' + 'to:' + u1756527447 + '@' + h1579790968 + '>' + linktext + '</a>');
